data.description: Seller is offering up to $10,000.00 in Seller Concessions!    Absolutely Charming 5bd 2ba Farmhouse on over an acre in Waterville! Enjoy the sweet front porch and serene surroundings. Bring your animals; Several livestock pens and run-in sheds and a chicken coop. Peaceful location 5 minutes from the town of Waterville. So many major updates on this property! New roof, new septic and a new well in 2010. Open concept kitchen / dining area. Spacious bedroom on main floor. Full bath with a new tub. Fresh paint throughout the interior of the house. Fenced back yard area with a porch and two outbuildings. Beautiful, fenced garden area. Unlimited potential at this lovely mini farm away from the hustle and bustle of the city!
